OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1784909938
OL,3,CCancer patient left to sleep on
OL,4,Cairport floor after flight cancellation
OL,6,FA terminal cancer patient has
OL,7,Fcriticised easyJet for his
OL,8,F"disgraceful treatment" after being
OL,9,Fleft to sleep on the floor at Gatwick
OL,10,FAirport when his flight was cancelled.
OL,12,FArmed forces veteran Wayne Lawson was
OL,13,Ftravelling back from the Canary
OL,14,FIslands in what he believes will be
OL,15,Fhis last holiday.
OL,17,FWayne was diagnosed with stage four
OL,18,Fterminal cancer in October 2024 and
OL,19,Fwas given between one and two years to
OL,20,Flive.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1784909938
OL,3,CCancer patient left to sleep on
OL,4,Cairport floor after flight cancellation
OL,6,FAfter his flight between Gatwick and
OL,7,FJersey was cancelled due to
OL,8,Fthunderstorms, Wayne and his friend
OL,9,Fhad to sleep on the terminal's floor
OL,10,Funtil the next morning.
OL,12,FWayne has now criticised easyJet for a
OL,13,Flack of support for special assistance
OL,14,Fpassengers.
OL,16,FEasyJet said in a statement that Wayne
OL,17,Fwas transferred to a flight the
OL,18,Ffollowing morning and apologised for
OL,19,Fthe incident.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1784909938
OL,3,CCancer patient left to sleep on
OL,4,Cairport floor after flight cancellation
OL,6,FOn Saturday 27 June, Wayne and his
OL,7,Ffriend arrived at the terminal just
OL,8,Fafter midday and waited in the special
OL,9,Fassistance lounge.
OL,11,FHowever, they soon learnt that their
OL,12,Fflights had been cancelled.
OL,14,F"At no point did anybody from easyJet
OL,15,Fcome over and see us," Wayne
OL,16,Fexplained. "I was more panicked
OL,17,Fbecause I'm thinking about my chemo.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1784909938
OL,3,CCancer patient left to sleep on
OL,4,Cairport floor after flight cancellation
OL,6,F"My friend went to an easyJet member
OL,7,Fand said, 'What do I do? My friend is
OL,8,Factually dying, he needs to get rest,
OL,9,Fhe needs to have his chemo'."
OL,11,FGround staff advised Wayne to arrange
OL,12,Fhis own hotel, despite airlines being
OL,13,Frequired to provide accommodation if
OL,14,Fpassengers are stranded overnight.
OL,16,FThe pair then discovered that there
OL,17,Fwere no hotels within a 15-mile radius
OL,18,Fof Gatwick, and no flights available
OL,19,Ffrom any other airports.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1784909938
OL,3,CCancer patient left to sleep on
OL,4,Cairport floor after flight cancellation
OL,6,FWithout any other option, Wayne and
OL,7,Fhis friend stayed on the terminal's
OL,8,Ffloor.
OL,10,F"It was absolutely horrible," Wayne
OL,11,Fsaid. "The (cancer) treatment that I
OL,12,Freceived destroyed my nerves in my
OL,13,Ffingertips and feet, so I have a high
OL,14,Fsensation.
OL,16,F"It's telling me that I'm in sheer
OL,17,Fagony constantly, but it's the damaged
OL,18,Fnerves telling my brain lies (...)
OL,19,Fhaving to sleep on the floor was
OL,20,Fhorrific.
OL,26,@sD@LpmsD@SpnzD@^pmzD@bpn
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1784909938
OL,3,CCancer patient left to sleep on
OL,4,Cairport floor after flight cancellation
OL,6,F"It's even worse when your hand
OL,7,Ftouches something cold; the pain
OL,8,Fshoots through you. I had to put a
OL,9,Fcouple of extra tops on and a summer
OL,10,Fjacket. It was just horrific."
OL,12,FAfter speaking to easyJet staff the
OL,13,Fnext day, Wayne managed to get the
OL,14,F8:30am flight out.
OL,16,FHowever, the Royal Navy veteran says
OL,17,Fhe is "disgusted" by how he was
OL,18,Ftreated, adding that other special
OL,19,Fassistance passengers were left in the
OL,20,Fsame situation as him.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1784909938
OL,3,CCancer patient left to sleep on
OL,4,Cairport floor after flight cancellation
OL,6,F"I'm here fighting for others as well
OL,7,F- they really need to treat people
OL,8,Fwith a bit more respect.
OL,10,F"What I would hope is that when there
OL,11,Fare delays, keep people who are asking
OL,12,Ffor special assistance in the loop,
OL,13,Fbecause where I think they failed (is
OL,14,Fthat able-bodied people) have a head
OL,15,Fstart on us that allows them to book
OL,16,Fhotels and sort themselves out.
OL,26,@uD@cpmvD@Xpn
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1784909938
OL,3,CCancer patient left to sleep on
OL,4,Cairport floor after flight cancellation
OL,6,F"EasyJet really should be stepping in
OL,7,Fthere. Get special assistance
OL,8,Fpassengers that help first. The
OL,9,Fairport gave me that help; easyJet let
OL,10,Fme down big time.
OL,12,F"I am fighting to stay alive, I don't
OL,13,Fneed to fight with easyJet."
OL,15,FIn a statement, easyJet said they have
OL,16,Fapologised to Wayne for his experience
OL,17,Fand refunded his flights as a "gesture
OL,18,Fof goodwill".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1784909938
OL,3,CCancer patient left to sleep on
OL,4,Cairport floor after flight cancellation
OL,6,F"We are very sorry to hear about Mr
OL,7,FLawson's circumstances and for the
OL,8,Fdifficulty he experienced on his
OL,9,Fjourney to Jersey after his flight was
OL,10,Fcancelled, due to thunderstorms
OL,11,Fsuspending operations at London
OL,12,FGatwick," the statement reads.
OL,14,F"The safety and wellbeing of our
OL,15,Fcustomers is always our highest
OL,16,Fpriority.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1784909938
OL,3,CCancer patient left to sleep on
OL,4,Cairport floor after flight cancellation
OL,6,F"We transferred Mr Lawson to a flight
OL,7,Fdeparting the following morning, and
OL,8,Fwhile we always aim to secure hotel
OL,9,Faccommodation for customers where
OL,10,Fneeded, as availability was limited,
OL,11,Fwe advised customers who booked their
OL,12,Fown that they would be reimbursed."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G10/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
